{"tid":932432,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"中學個陣拍拖係最珍貴既回憶","createTime":"2018-12-07T17:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T00:39:12.000Z","uid":136933,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71ad5919c245f1b3ce609eebd6efbdbeb8e9b283","tid":932432,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:30:23.000Z","msg":"諗返起之前中學拍拖<br />\n個種無憂無慮已經搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLunch 同佢食個飯 同佢一齊放學<br />\n同佢一齊轉班房上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  VA堂一齊畫畫<br />\nPE堂望住佢打波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放學佢等住我抄手冊 再係附近文具舖或者屋村商場行下<br />\nSport day 旅行一齊影即影即有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢種平淡既幸福 大個就好難體會返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個陣既世界有佢之餘 仲有好多朋友同學 學業一齊兼顧<br />\n生活好美滿同充實<br />\n爭執都冇咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升左大學拍拖啲時間多左<br />\n啲心機擺多左 交都鬧多左<br />\n好似無辦法真心真意愛上一個人<br />\n愛情變得不再單純"},{"pid":"3f8bb049b9f2aaaed05364c5c2a7370a00d0e2c1","tid":932432,"uid":101253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"中學無拍拖真係人生一大憾事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5083ca5244beca290c7ee023246643589cb35279","tid":932432,"uid":189336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c2c0b36b82e0c8aa4e25f652030b887979c7c2f","tid":932432,"uid":136933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f8bb049b9f2aaaed05364c5c2a7370a00d0e2c1","tid":932432,"uid":101253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"中學無拍拖真係人生一大憾事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:33:34.000Z","msg":"人生冇左個經歷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1ea2